document_data.name: Aswansea
document_data.mainbody: '''Aswansea''' was a [[moon elf]] [[priest]] of [[Tyr]] inhabiting the city of [[Daggerford]] in the [[Western Heartlands]] during the mid-to-late 14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Activities: Aswansea was a member of the [[Daggerford militia]] and led patrols through the countryside.{{Cite interactive atlas|3990 Daggerford}}
document_data.History: She originally wanted to be a [[ranger]], but always fell behind her peers during hikes. Her parents were among the moon elves who resided at [[Floshin Estates]].
document_data.Relationships: She was close friends with [[Maelwyn]]. Aswansea was in a tentative relationship with [[Cork (Daggerford)|Cork]], but ultimately did not want to marry him because he was a "short-lived" [[human]].
